  "body": "As discussed on the Nov 4 planning call, we determined it would be good to have a dashboard to look at very specific parameters of the node to ensure it is safe for release. This will also supplement some sort of standardized way to look at metrics between engineers and allow us to quickly observe critical metrics that will help determine whether or not a release is safe to go out. \r\n\r\nWe should figure out the process that each engineer uses to look at metrics data and compile them into a Release Dashboard, which will also serve as a checklist for us.",
